                                            <p><span class="excerpt-inner">Could Pearl Harbor be called a &#x201C;failure of imagination,&#x201D; and in that sense was it similar to the attacks of 9/11?</span><a href="//opinionator.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/03/27/the-certainty-of-donald-rumsfeld-part-3/"
                                                    class="more-link">Read&#xA0;more&#x2026;</a></p>
